    "This methodical approach helps AI to interact dynamically with data, assess it intelligibly, and provide human-like, contextually appropriate responses.",
    "The three basic components of RAG are designed to handle more complex questions & provide users with very customized and more relevant information, thereby serving as the ideal foundation for member portals in medical settings.",
    "Seek: Retrieving comes first in the RAG process.",
    "During this phase, the artificial intelligence system searches the most relevant records or documents needed to answer a query or fix a problem.",
